f29a14","tid":746122,"uid":54733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:36:48.000Z","msg":"粵港澳大灣區將成第二矽谷 企業爭搶先機<br />\n<br />\n英國著名雜誌《經濟學人》早前大篇幅報導，深圳已成為矽洲（Silicon Delta），與美國的矽谷（Silicon Valley）可以比擬，其實中央政府戰略眼光更闊，要將深圳、香港加上珠三角其它9個城市發展為粵港澳大灣區，要與美國包括矽谷的三藩市大灣區、日本東京灣區並排，成為中國經濟未來發展的重要帶動力，其中重中之重，是要將之建成創新科技的大灣區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/800067-%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%9F%BD%E8%B0%B7-%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%88%AD%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fmacau%2Farticle%2F800067-%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%259F%25BD%25E8%25B0%25B7-%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2590%25B6%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%25A9%259F&d=cdjQsK2mD6yhG1gQ%2Fe%2Fj%2BYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4e1d6d26\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/800067-%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%9F%BD%E8%B0%B7-%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%88%AD%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粵港澳大灣區好快超越矽谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd3d2bd0458da2e8d1d4e4f30fad06a63d2db89","tid":746122,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"8faba132e6ff1f637db24babe49d64457a8012df","tid":746122,"uid":118509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:27:11.000Z","msg":"突然諗起子華講過，九七回歸，你唔講我唔講，中央就唔記得架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa